Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,過這邊來\N{\rENG}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:36.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是美國的問題所在\N{\rENG}This is the problem. this is what's wrong with America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,它變得太大  大到讓人迷失自我\N{\rENG}It's gotten so big, you just can't find your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:45.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,從前街角的雜貨鋪現在變成了超市\N{\rENG}The grocery store on the corner is now a supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,糖果店變成了麥當勞\N{\rENG}The candy store is a mcdonald's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:54.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有這裡  他媽的超級折扣店\N{\rENG}And this place, a super-fucking discount store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,作為私營業主的那種自豪哪去了?\N{\rENG}Where's the pride of ownership, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,私人服務哪去了?\N{\rENG}Where's the personal service?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,懂我意思嗎  操\N{\rENG}You see what I mean? shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們哪來的權力去砍掉供應商\N{\rENG}I mean, what right do they have, of cutting out the suppliers,
