Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,從廠家手裡直接訂貨?\N{\rENG}Buying direct from the manufacturer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,索尼  東芝\N{\rENG}Sony this, toshiba that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:33.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些黃種人搶走了美國人的飯碗\N{\rENG}All them chinks putting Americans out of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是現實\N{\rENG}That's the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?\N{\rENG}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你無法找到問題的癥結\N{\rENG}You can't find the heart of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,也根本無從下手去解決問題\N{\rENG}To stick the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人嗎?\N{\rENG}Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能幫你嗎?\N{\rENG}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:03.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,叫救護車\N{\rENG}Call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,別麻煩了  弗蘭克\N{\rENG}Forget it, frank.
