Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,叫救護車\N{\rENG}Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人說邦比·強森是個好人\N{\rENG}Some say bumpy johnson was a great man,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,他的頌詞中說他是個樂善好施的人\N{\rENG}According to the eulogies, a giving man,
