Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒人在他們的悼詞中\N{\rENG}No one chose to use in their remembrances
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,把邦比·強森\N{\rENG}The word most often associated with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,和黑幫頭目聯繫在一起\N{\rENG}Ellsworth "bumpy" johnson, "gangster,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,在這個寒冷的下午  邦比·強森蓋棺論定\N{\rENG}Whose passing has brought a who's who of mourners on this chilly afternoon.
