Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,尼克  尼克\N{\rENG}Nicky! nicky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,政界的精英們也紛紛出動\N{\rENG}From the political arena,
