Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,在我的葬禮上我想要雞翅\N{\rENG}I want chicken wings at my funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,尼克·巴恩斯  瞧瞧是誰來了?\N{\rENG}All right, nicky barnes. who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,他不知道是什麼打中了他\N{\rENG}He didn't know what hit him, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只管對著他的臉不停開槍\N{\rENG}I just kept popping him in the face 'cause that's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有火  你有火嗎?\N{\rENG}I don't have a lighter. you have a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,還行吧?\N{\rENG}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rENG}That's very good.
