Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,順便幫我去拿個火\N{\rENG}Go get me a light while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝了\N{\rENG}Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,卡塔諾\N{\rENG}Don cattano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,羅斯  你好嗎?\N{\rENG}Hey, how you doing, rossi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rENG}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,要杯酒麼先生?\N{\rENG}Would you like a drink, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,給他杯威士卡加冰\N{\rENG}Give him a scotch on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,過來\N{\rENG}Come on. come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克  我知道你不好受\N{\rENG}I know you're hurting, frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也不好過\N{\rENG}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N{\rENG}I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你真沒事?  -是的\N{\rENG}You gonna be all right? yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,我確定邦比沒對你說起  但他要我保證\N{\rENG}I'm sure bumpy didn't say anything to you, but he made me promise
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果他出事了\N{\rENG}That if anything ever happened to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我將保證你衣食無憂\N{\rENG}That I should make sure that you want for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常感謝\N{\rENG}I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,在這個房間有一半的人都欠邦比的錢\N{\rENG}You know, half the people in this room owed bumpy money when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:40.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們以為我會忘記  但我會把帳收回來\N{\rENG}They think I'm gonna forget to collect, but I'm gonna get that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,哦  精神可嘉  放手去做吧\N{\rENG}Well, that's the spirit. go get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:50.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,羅伯特先生  到起訴席就坐\N{\rENG}Mr. roberts, taking the prosecution's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:55.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,告訴我們物證  辯論  判斷是什麼\N{\rENG}Give us us v. mead, subject, issues, what the determination was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,和這些東西對我們意味著什麼\N{\rENG}And what it means to us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:02.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,同學們請注意聽  你們將要質詢羅伯特先生\N{\rENG}Class, you'll be critiquing Mr. roberts, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,我討厭被叫到名字\N{\rENG}I hate hearing my name called, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,那意味著我要站到前面去  轉過身\N{\rENG}It means I gotta get up in front of the class, I gotta turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,而且我明白他們每個人都知道的比我多\N{\rENG}And I know every one of those people there, they know more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:18.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,人最怕的不是死亡而是當眾演講\N{\rENG}The number one fear of people, it ain't dying, it's public speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,這讓我我身體不舒服  我想吐\N{\rENG}I get physically ill, I wanna throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,這可是你謀生之路啊\N{\rENG}And that's what you wanna do for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想那樣  我想閃人\N{\rENG}No, I don't wanna be like that, man, I wanna beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼  這次我來做?\N{\rENG}So, should I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  我來  我們高中就認識了\N{\rENG}No, he'll take it from me, he knows me. I've known him since high school.
