Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.12,1:37:24.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,他的名字是弗蘭克·盧卡斯\N{\rENG}His name is frank lucas.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.69,1:37:27.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,原籍加州北部的格林斯博羅\N{\rENG}Originally from greensboro, north carolina.
