Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.57,1:38:20.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,少點吧  不然我換地方  怎麼樣\N{\rENG}Oh, man, I'm gonna take it somewhere else, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.28,1:38:23.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些店面都是毒品交易的配送中心\N{\rENG}These businesses are the distribution and collection points
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.48,1:38:26.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,同時也都是弗蘭克名義上的收入來源\N{\rENG}For frank's dope and frank's money.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.62,1:38:29.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,所有關於弗蘭克的資料都讓他看起來\N{\rENG}Everything about frank's life seems
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.29,1:38:31.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼的謙遜  有規矩  守法\N{\rENG}Unpretentious, orderly and legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.82,1:38:34.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,他每天都早上五點就起床\N{\rENG}He starts early, gets up at 5:00 a.m.
