Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.22,1:39:35.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,邦比每天都要見到他\N{\rENG}The guy he sees every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.38,1:39:37.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,就像義大利的家族黑幫一樣\N{\rENG}It's like a sicilian family.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.82,1:39:41.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,他也用同樣的組織結構來保護自己\N{\rENG}He's structured his organization to protect him in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.99,1:39:43.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果他跟了邦比很長時間\N{\rENG}And if he was with bumpy for so long,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.49,1:39:46.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,那就說明他和那些義大利人的來往肯定很密切\N{\rENG}That means he would have spent a lot of time with italians.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.20,1:39:48.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,密切到對他們的做法瞭若指掌\N{\rENG}Definitely long enough to learn that much.
