Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.17,1:57:31.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有足夠的條件養育孩子\N{\rENG}Being around me is no place for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.71,1:57:34.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,你把他帶到維加斯去吧  我有空就去看他\N{\rENG}You take him to vegas. I'll come see him when I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.88,1:57:41.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,法官  很抱歉浪費了法庭的時間\N{\rENG}Your honor, I want to apologize for wasting the court's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.40,1:57:55.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,德克\N{\rENG}Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.20,1:57:56.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我看見他們了\N{\rENG}I see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.70,1:57:58.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,他來了\N{\rENG}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.72,1:58:18.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在做什麼?\N{\rENG}The fuck is this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.12,1:58:20.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,喂  香檳\N{\rENG}Hey! champagne.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.56,1:58:22.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,-聖誕快樂  -給我們的?\N{\rENG}Merry christmas, detectives. for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.86,1:58:24.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  好好享受吧\N{\rENG}Yeah. enjoy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.06,1:58:27.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,玩得開心點\N{\rENG}You fellas have a good time. mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.80,1:58:30.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是克裡斯托在作現場報導\N{\rENG}It's cristal.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.20,1:58:36.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,南越部隊召來飛機進行轟炸\N{\rENG}South vietnamese troops called in air strikes
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.61,1:58:39.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,攻擊市內的共產黨的據點\N{\rENG}On communist positions inside the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.04,1:58:43.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,按潛規則辦事  這是一回事\N{\rENG}Paying off johnny law, that's one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.85,1:58:45.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,這本來不是什麼問題\N{\rENG}There ain't no problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.55,1:58:48.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我十歲起就一直在給員警錢\N{\rENG}I've been paying off the police since I was 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.35,1:58:51.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,把他們的孩子送到大學  獲得國家榮譽獎章\N{\rENG}Put more of their kids through college than the national merit award.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.15,1:58:52.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個又一個...\N{\rENG}Give me one of them round one... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.02,1:58:54.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,這次有點不同...\N{\rENG}This is different, though. these...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.06,1:58:58.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們是專門調查組的  這完全是他們自己的問題\N{\rENG}Special investigative unit. that's their problem. they think they're special.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.06,1:59:01.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,雜種  一點職業道德都沒有\N{\rENG}Fucking crooks. no code of ethics.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.83,1:59:02.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,你看怎麼樣?\N{\rENG}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.97,1:59:05.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了\N{\rENG}Looks great. it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.40,1:59:06.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.14,1:59:09.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我擔心的並不只有員警\N{\rENG}The police, that ain't the only somebody I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.30,1:59:12.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我看到不認識的人和車\N{\rENG}I seeing cars where I ain't never seen them before, people I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.41,1:59:13.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rENG}Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.06,1:59:18.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂  查理\N{\rENG}Merry christmas, charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.36,1:59:19.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.56,1:59:20.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\rENG}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.00,1:59:22.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也愛你\N{\rENG}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.80,1:59:25.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,拿下這個\N{\rENG}Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.90,1:59:27.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我吃一片麵包  馬上就走\N{\rENG}A quick toast, and then I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.94,1:59:30.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,這裡發生的事情是一場戰爭意外\N{\rENG}What happened here was an accident of war.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.44,1:59:32.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人犯了錯誤\N{\rENG}Somebody made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.81,1:59:36.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,邦比很久沒有出來過了\N{\rENG}Bumpy ain't hardly ever go out no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.18,1:59:38.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,從某個時候開始  他就待在家裡\N{\rENG}After a certain point he stayed in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.19,1:59:43.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,看電視\N{\rENG}Watch tv.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.66,1:59:46.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,下棋  看報紙\N{\rENG}Play chess. read the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.29,1:59:50.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想他只是想過點安靜的生活\N{\rENG}I thought he was just trying to lead the quiet life,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.50,1:59:52.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,但實際上  他哪也不能去\N{\rENG}But no, he couldn't go nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.66,1:59:54.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,哪都不安全\N{\rENG}Not without something happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.30,1:59:55.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克...\N{\rENG}Frankie...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.97,1:59:57.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們仍然可以出去\N{\rENG}We can still go out.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.74,1:59:59.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,和誰? 到哪裡?\N{\rENG}With who? where?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.47,2:00:01.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,和...\N{\rENG}Well, with...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.27,2:00:02.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,但有人在監視他\N{\rENG}But I know he's under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.04,2:00:05.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許再也不能和我家人\N{\rENG}Ain't gonna be no christmas time
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.88,2:00:07.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,這裡一起過聖誕了\N{\rENG}With my family being here no more.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.71,2:00:10.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,你給他們錢不就完了嗎?\N{\rENG}Why don't you just pay who you have to pay?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.95,2:00:13.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,給了  上百上千萬的錢\N{\rENG}I do pay them. I pay thousands and millions
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.22,2:00:15.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,給小毒販  員警\N{\rENG}To dope dealers, crooks, cops.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.79,2:00:16.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,每個人我都給\N{\rENG}I pay everybody.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.02,2:00:18.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我付的比他們應得的多\N{\rENG}I pay more than they should get.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.22,2:00:20.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,但他們從來不知足!\N{\rENG}I can't satisfy nobody!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.49,2:00:22.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,就像吸毒一樣! 每個人都很歇斯底里!\N{\rENG}It's like dope! everybody's strung out!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.66,2:00:24.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,你給的越多  他們就要的越多\N{\rENG}The more you give 'em, the more they want.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.83,2:00:27.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們總是想多要點\N{\rENG}They expect more.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.13,2:00:30.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,弄成惡性循環了\N{\rENG}Give more and they want more.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.04,2:00:37.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想出去嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you want to go out?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.08,2:00:40.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的  穿上衣服\N{\rENG}All right, baby. put something of what you got.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.15,2:00:41.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,-我? -對\N{\rENG}Should i? yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.45,2:00:42.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是聖誕精神\N{\rENG}That's christmas spirit.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.75,2:00:44.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就對了嘛\N{\rENG}That's what I'm talking about. feliz navidad.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.08,2:00:46.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,穿漂亮點兒\N{\rENG}Something nice? mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.56,2:00:55.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們將會過得很愉快\N{\rENG}We're going to have a great time.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.99,2:00:57.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  淇塔\N{\rENG}That's right, chica.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.20,2:00:59.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,盧卡斯  祝您愉快\N{\rENG}Mr. lucas. enjoy your evening.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.80,2:01:02.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在沒什麼狀況了\N{\rENG}It's all clear.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.72,2:01:07.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\rENG}Nicky!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.55,2:01:09.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,那是誰? 是你的人尼克  看見了嗎?\N{\rENG}Who is that? there's your boy, nicky. see him?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.46,2:01:10.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,看見了嗎?\N{\rENG}Know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.56,2:01:13.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我看見了  繼續開\N{\rENG}Yeah, I see him. let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.89,2:01:14.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,要轉回來嗎?\N{\rENG}Around back?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.06,2:01:18.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,不要  我不會偷偷溜進我自己的俱樂部\N{\rENG}Hell, no. I ain't sneaking into my own club.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.57,2:01:20.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,難以置信\N{\rENG}Incredible. huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.76,2:01:44.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\rENG}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.03,2:01:48.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rENG}Hold on. hold on.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.50,2:01:57.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦?\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.67,2:01:59.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想在車裡等\N{\rENG}I want to wait in the car.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.57,2:02:02.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克  讓我去弄就行了\N{\rENG}Frank, I got it. I got it. I'll wait for it. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.04,2:02:05.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,要那種黃色的醬  黃色的\N{\rENG}Get that yellow sauce. yellow sauce.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.21,2:02:07.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有雞  宮爆雞丁\N{\rENG}And the chicken. the kung pao chicken.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.52,2:02:15.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,把暖氣打開好嗎?\N{\rENG}Can you turn the heater on?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.60,2:02:23.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,該死  我去拿鑰匙\N{\rENG}Shit. I'm gonna go get the keys.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.71,2:02:40.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,-德克  把鑰匙給我  -給你\N{\rENG}Doc, give me the keys. here you go.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.99,2:02:47.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,德克!\N{\rENG}Doc!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.39,2:02:53.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,快下車\N{\rENG}Get out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.63,2:03:01.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你還好嗎? -沒事\N{\rENG}You okay? yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.67,2:03:02.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,該死的\N{\rENG}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.07,2:03:06.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼樣?\N{\rENG}Come on, baby. you all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.07,2:03:08.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們走\N{\rENG}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.03,2:03:30.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,是尼克幹的?\N{\rENG}Was it nicky?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.17,2:03:34.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,不管是不是他幹的  我們馬上去殺了他\N{\rENG}We'll go right now and fucking kill him whether it was him or not,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.64,2:03:36.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,只要你下一個命令  弗蘭克\N{\rENG}You say the word, frankie.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.11,2:03:40.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得有所行動\N{\rENG}We got to do something, frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.87,2:03:41.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能光坐在這裡\N{\rENG}We can't just sit here.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.01,2:03:43.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們要走了\N{\rENG}We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.65,2:03:48.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家都回去吧\N{\rENG}All right, everybody get out. you all right, man?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.45,2:03:50.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,今天是耶誕節  去和家人待在一塊\N{\rENG}Go on home. it's christmas time. go and be with your families.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.68,2:03:51.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\rENG}I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.12,2:03:55.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,走呀  去陪你們的孩子\N{\rENG}Go on. go ahead. be with your kids.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.16,2:03:56.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rENG}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.64,2:04:09.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡?\N{\rENG}Where are we gonna go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.84,2:04:11.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們去西班牙  或者  中國?\N{\rENG}We're gonna go to spain, somewhere? china?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.54,2:04:15.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,別鬧了  坐下  說說你想去哪\N{\rENG}Huh? come on, sit down. tell me where you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.71,2:04:18.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克  我們哪都可以去\N{\rENG}Frank, we can go anywhere we want.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.75,2:04:20.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,-不行  -我們在哪生活都行  弗蘭克\N{\rENG}No, we can't. we can live anywhere, frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.75,2:04:22.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,去哪裡? 然後呢? 逃跑? 躲藏?\N{\rENG}Where? and do what? run? hide?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.55,2:04:25.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克·盧卡斯不會怕任何人\N{\rENG}Frank lucas don't run from nobody, baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.59,2:04:27.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們哪裡也不去  就在這裡待著\N{\rENG}We ain't going nowhere. we're gonna stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.52,2:04:29.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我的家\N{\rENG}We're gonna stay right here. this is my home.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.89,2:04:33.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的生意  我的妻子  母親和家庭都在這裡\N{\rENG}This is where my business is, my wife, my mother, my family.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.33,2:04:35.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我的國家  我哪也不去\N{\rENG}My country. I ain't going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.50,2:04:38.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會因為怕任何人而逃離\N{\rENG}I ain't running from nobody!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.07,2:04:41.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是美國\N{\rENG}This is America.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.51,2:04:51.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也得留在這裡!\N{\rENG}And you ain't going nowhere, either!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.11,2:04:54.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,啊?\N{\rENG}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.55,2:04:59.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,華盛頓時間27日7點\N{\rENG}A ceasefire, internationally supervised, will begin
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.35,2:05:03.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,停火協議將會生效\N{\rENG}At 7:00 p.m. this saturday, january 27th, washington time.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.76,2:05:05.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,我一會給你打電話\N{\rENG}I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.06,2:05:08.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,喂! 你在做什麼?\N{\rENG}Hey! what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.50,2:05:11.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑞奇\N{\rENG}Richie.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.91,2:05:23.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽說科西嘉黑幫朝弗蘭克開了一槍\N{\rENG}So, what I hear it was the corsican mob took a shot at frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.84,2:05:25.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,是法國販毒集團在美國的人幹的 菲爾南多·雷\N{\rENG}You know, french connection, fernando rey,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.78,2:05:28.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個被弗蘭克擠出了市場的毒販\N{\rENG}The exporters that frank has put out of business.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.55,2:05:31.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,在紐約我可以搞定\N{\rENG}Look, I can take care of him in new york.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.79,2:05:33.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是我不想總是擔心\N{\rENG}I just don't want to have to worry that every time
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.39,2:05:34.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,每次他開車過橋去澤西的時候\N{\rENG}He drives across the bridge to jersey,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.96,2:05:37.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,可能會被人暗殺\N{\rENG}Someone's gonna take another shot at him.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.89,2:05:41.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑞奇  我們得一起合作\N{\rENG}Richie, you and I gotta start working together.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.63,2:05:43.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們需要更加努力\N{\rENG}We need to step up our efforts.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.36,2:05:47.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,下次他們的槍法會更准\N{\rENG}Next time, their aim could be better.
